什么。</span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 20.3px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><br></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 20.3px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><br></p><p class=\"p3\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s3\">找下一个要买的东西，</span></p><p class=\"p3\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s3\">环视四周的眼睛一定是炯炯有神的吧。</span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 20.3px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><br></p><p class=\"p3\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s3\">“下一个是最后一个。”</span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 20.3px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><br></p><p class=\"p3\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s3\">买了关着烟花的瑜伽。</span></p><p class=\"p3\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s3\">除掉的话好像随时都可以看烟花。</span></p><p class=\"p3\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s3\">是像线香烟花那样的小类型吗？</span></p><p class=\"p3\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s3\">是像烟花一样大的类型吗？</span></p><p class=\"p3\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;\"><span class=\"s3\">这么说来马上就是生日了。</span></p><p class=\"p3\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-stretch: normal; li